title.narrative: Egypt Enhancing Access to Finance for Micro and Small Enterprises

description.narrative: The Project's development objective is to contribute to increased access to finance for micro and small enterprises on a sustainable and commercial basis, thus promoting growth, job creation, and an inclusive financial system, as well as ease the impact of the global economic crisis on micro and small enterprises.
